{
  "newspaper_id": "lankadeepa-lk",
  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/latest_news/\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda-\u0db4\u0dc0\u0dca-\u0db4\u0ddc\u0da9\u0dd2-\u0db8\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda-\u0d87\u0d9f-\u0d8b\u0da9-\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd9\u0dca-\u0d87\u0dba\u0dd2-/1-618937",
  "time_ut": 1661756425,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0db4\u0dc0\u0dca \u0db4\u0ddc\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d87\u0d9f \u0d8b\u0da9 \u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd9\u0dca \u0d87\u0dba\u0dd2?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Why put the sins of the rulers on the body of the little man?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Vijitha Herath, Gampaha District Member of the National People's Power, said in the Parliament that the Electricity Board is suffering losses due to the wrong policy decisions of the rulers and the common poor people of the country are now responsible for those sins.",
        "Mr. Vijitha Herath said that the people cannot be held accountable for the mistakes of the rulers and said that the rulers who took wrong decisions are at large while the poor people are suffering.",
        "The MP also said that as a result of wrong policies and various actions of politicians, the prices of not only electricity but also gas, fuel etc. are increasing.",
        "Mr. Vijitha Herath said this while addressing the parliamentary adjournment debate on electricity bill increase."
      ],
